- title = "No to war / Нет войне!"
- description = "Don't be a vatnik"
- content_for :title do
  = title
- content_for :meta_description do
  = description

- content_for :head do
  = render "shared/meta_tags", title: title, description: description, url: no_to_war_url, image: 'ua.jpg'

%div{class: "v2-elevated my-6 max-w-3xl"}
  %h1{class: "v2-page-title mb-4"}= title
  %p{class: "text-lg text-ink mb-3"}
    Hello
    %span{class: "flags flags-ru ml-1 mr-0"}
    and
    %span{class: "flags flags-by ml-1 mr-0"}
    friends, it's been too long.
  %p{class: "text-lg text-ink mb-3"}
    Two rules.
  %p{class: "text-lg text-ink mb-3"}
    1. We can't accept payments, so no premium servers. (if you've ever paid for premium,
    %a{href: "https://discord.gg/0s38RdItLiCmARMm"}
      contact us on discord
    for a free extension)
    %br
    2. Don't be a vatnik

  %p{class: "text-lg text-ink"}
    = form_tag do |form|
      = check_box_tag :not_a_vatnik, 'true'
      %label{for: 'not_a_vatnik', class: "ml-2 text-ink"}
        I am not a vatnik
      %br
      = submit_tag "Submit", class: "v2-btn v2-btn-primary mt-3"
